Author: fuckwhywhywhy
Text: Awkward laughter. That’s my only response when people comment on how skinny I am

Author: lostmyshitinamuseum
Text: It’s such a strange feeling, something similar happened to me. I was chatting with my boss and told her I’d been to a taco buffet and had 8 tacos. She then was like “8?! You had 8 tacos?! But you’re the skinniest one in the entire corporation!!”   How the heck do you respond to that
